{"title" : "周末一日军营生活体验（周五晚、周六全天，提前一周报名）" ,"content":"<P class=pa-8 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>军营体验是专为青少年打造的拓展项目套餐之一。以全封闭式军事化训练特点而著称。日常生活均采用部队的军事化生活管理办法。纪律与服从是军营集训的第一要旨。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-8 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>军营体验融入了与青少年成长教育相匹配的拓展训练活动及内务训练活动。孩子们需要克服日常懒散的生活习惯、融入部队集体军事化的生活当中来，通过各项拓展活动的集体配合，培养孩子们的自立与团队荣誉感，同时军营生活可培养孩子们良好的日常生活习惯。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;套餐内拓展项目简介：</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1><BR></SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>短时军训：早操军训时间设置为30-60分钟，为短时军训。以完成团队分配、破冰、团队口号及队长等准备为首要任务。其次进行队列制式动作的训练。目的是端正姿态，保持严整的团队阵容，养成令行禁止和严格遵守纪律的习惯，培养迅速、准确、协调一致的作风，为执行其他项目培训打下良好的基础。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>军营生活体验：选择军营拓展的企业，员工需提前一晚到达军营，以适应军营的生活节奏与氛</SPAN></P><P class=pa-5 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>围。在军营拓展期间，生活与内务完全采用部队军事化管理，从晨间出操、餐饮、</SPAN></P><P class=pa-6 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>作息、生活用品整理、均与部队战士相同管理办法。真正体验军营整齐、统一、服从的纪律风范。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>拓展训练：金牌上百种拓展活动，根据青少年特点，进行筛选。通过这些拓展活动的开展，有效的达成青少年对合作与团队精神的理解！常言说：“身教胜于言传”，在活动中，让青少年通过切身的体会，感受到来自于团队的力量，并对自身力量与极限有更直观的认识。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>总结分享：通过一日军营体营，组织青少年团队进行自我总结与心得分享。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1><BR></SPAN></P><P class=pa-14 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>报名参加办法：</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>提前一周报名，满10人成班，详情电话咨询。</SPAN></P>"}